translate portuguese u19a2s1c_95907875:

    # cw "You've kept me imprisoned for too long! I will never love you, Terry! I'm leaving!"
    cw "Mantiveste-me presa durante demasiado tempo! Nunca te amarei, Terry! Vou-me embora!"

